project.name: mdeditor
project.description: Small description for mdeditor goes here

md-button-modal.name: md-button-modal
md-button-modal.description:
mdEditor Component that renders a button which displays a modal
dialog when clicked.

md-boolean.name: md-boolean
md-boolean.description: Input, edit, display a boolean value

md-codelist.name: md-codelist
md-codelist.description:
Specialized select list control for displaying and selecting
options in mdCodes codelists.
Access to codelists is provided by the 'codelist' service.
Descriptions of all codes (tooltips) are embedded within the codelists.

md-codelist-multi.name: md-codelist-multi
md-codelist-multi.description:
Specialized select list control for displaying and selecting
options in mdCodes codelists.
Extends md-codelist.
Allows selection of multiple options.

md-datetime.name: md-datetime
md-datetime.description:
Datetime control with dropdown calendar.
Based on Bootstrap datetime picker.

md-input.name: md-input
md-input.description: Input, edit, display a single item

md-inputs.name: md-inputs
md-inputs.description: Input, edit, display an array of strings

md-select.name: md-select
md-select.description:
A select list control for displaying and selecting options
provided in an array or promise array.

md-textarea.name: md-textarea
md-textarea.description: Input, edit, display a multi-line, expandable, text area.

md-address.name: md-address
md-address.description: mdEditor class for input and edit of mdJSON address objects.

md-object-table.name: md-object-table
md-object-table.description:
mdEditor class for managing a table of similar mdJSON objects
for selection for edit or deletion.
The class is configurable for reuse with mdJSON object arrays.

md-online-resource-array.name: md-online-resource-array
md-online-resource-array.description:
mdEditor class for input and edit of mdJSON 'onlineResource' object
arrays.
The class manages the maintenance of an array of online resource
objects using the md-object-table class.

md-phone-array.name: md-phone-array
md-phone-array.description:
mdEditor class for input and edit of mdJSON 'phone' object.
The class manages the maintenance of an array of phone objects.
